ighties please, if you kill a lighty for a good reason, fine.  (for a spawn or they talked @#%$ etc) Darky and 4team guilds are KoS, unless it is someone you know and YOU don't wanna attack them.  Ports and Revives/rez's and trades are fine with anyone on dark or 4team.  Do not Corpse Camp, Do not Exp kill, Do not Bind Rush, don't be lame, its a simple request.  If you die PvP its your job to ask if you must scoot or if you can stay, you work it out with your killer(s), vice versa if you kill someone.  <br><br>PvE rules: Guild loot will work as such, need before greed, a Raid consists of 2 or more gorups, complete or not.  If not more than 7 people, and its all guildys, it is considered group loot, and everyone there decides how loot works.  If you lose roll dont bitch plz.  There will be a wish list, you can put down item(s) you really really want, 3 total.  Depending how often you attend raids and how well of a reputation you give the guild, the more likely you are to get that/those items.  Need before greed, but if someone attends 20 raids (just an example) and an item drops that is better than they got, but not super better, and someone how has been in guild for just as long but only goes on hate raids or something like that, the other person WILL get it, because they are more valuable to the family.  I want a guild that when someone sees in a zone they say &quot;hail &lt;guildname here&gt; say hello to everyone for me&quot;  and people invite us to raids just because of our integrity.<br><br>Thats what i expect this guild to be, a family guild, everyone is down to help everyone, we are fair with each other, help each other, RESPECT each other.  Do not lie, steal, cheat, or bitch, for any reason.  I understand the need to complain once in a while, but do not bitch (if you cannot define bitching to yourself, dont even think about this could-be-guild)<br><br>My name is Bruski Skoaldiak, I often play my Iksar to escape some high level politics, his name is Evandor, send me a tell if you are interested.  Post here if you want and ill search for you in game.<br><br>As far as names go, I havent been good at coming up with names, and these rules are far from complete...this is just a rough outline.<br><br>Thanks for reading<br><br>edit: the name has been decided, enough people are down to get it off the ground, should see us running aorund in a few weeks or so <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ubruskithebeerman.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bruski The Beer man</A> at: 12/31/01 9:38:01 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ubruskithebeerman.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bruski The Beer man</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(1/4/02 5:15:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=497.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Combine Alliance</span><hr size=1> for more information visit <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub50.ezboard.com/bbeerland">pub50.ezboard.com/bbeerland</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p>Bruski, Bruha, Evandor, Bruttis, Bruslee<BR>Skoaldiak Attack!!<BR>I am the Alpha to the Seventh Power, Omega in its Last Hours, of Intrical Towers and Meteor Showers, All things Devoured, Expose the Cowards, Chaos and Power, The Devil is yours, the Lord is Ours!</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showPrevMessage?topicID=497.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showNextMessage?topicID=497.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub77.e